headline: Synopsys tops revenue estimates on strong demand for chip design tools

Synopsys, whose software is used by semiconductor firms to design ‚Äåand verify chips, has benefited from surging investment in artificial intelligence and advanced computing, which require increasingly complex chip architectures.  It has also been benefiting from its partnership with Nvidia, Intel and Qualcomm.
